\par {\b Requirements}
\par Bomb riot requires a colour palette of at least 256 colours and should run best, or at least be most playable, in 640x480 resolution.
\par 
\par {\b The Game}
\par Bomb Riot is a game for up to four players.  Players run around a maze dropping bombs, trying to destroy each other.  The winner of a game is the last player left alive.  The winner of a match is the first player to win a specified number of games.  Once 
a match is completed, there is an option to continue.  The continue option allows the winning player to receive a random bonus which will be available to that player at the start of every game of the next match.
\par 
